OL,3,CCrowd boos former Liverpool goalkeeper
OL,4,Cfor saving boy's penalty - twice
OL,6,FCrowds booed former Liverpool
OL,7,Fgoalkeeper David James after he saved
OL,8,Fa schoolboy's half-time penalty -
OL,9,Ftwice.
OL,11,FThe 54 year old, who played for the
OL,12,Freds between 1992 and 1999, returned
OL,13,Fto Anfield for a community engagement
OL,14,Fprogramme where fans get the chance to
OL,15,Fscore at the Kop end.
OL,17,FBut the goalie seemed to be taking his
OL,18,Fjob too seriously when the boy,
OL,19,Fthought to be only 11 years old,
OL,20,Fstepped up to the penalty spot.
