OL,3,CCrowd boos former Liverpool goalkeeper
OL,4,Cfor saving boy's penalty - twice
OL,6,FThe young lad took his big moment in
OL,7,Ffront of a crowd of more than 60,000
OL,8,Fpeople half way through Sunday's 2-1
OL,9,Fwin over Chelsea, only to be denied by
OL,10,FJames.
OL,12,FHe was then given the chance to retake
OL,13,Fhis penalty but, adding insult to
OL,14,Finjury, James dived stopping the ball
OL,15,Fwith his foot before it could reach
OL,16,Fthe back of the net.
OL,18,FReports suggest the youngster was
OL,19,F"absolutely gutted" to have his dream
OL,20,Fblocked, while supporters were divided
OL,21,Fin their response.
