OL,6,FHowever, YouTuber Paul Machin was in
OL,7,Fno doubt as he filmed the scenario
OL,8,Fplaying out on the pitch.
OL,10,F"The amount of things he let in in
OL,11,Fthat goal as an actual paid Liverpool
OL,12,Fplayer!" he commented.
OL,14,FThe boy shrugged his shoulders after
OL,15,Fthe incident but appeared to forgive
OL,16,FJames.
OL,18,FThe pair shook hands and hugged as a
OL,19,Fmuted applause echoed around the
OL,20,Fstadium.
